Rekayasa Industri Jobs: 7 Positions
PT Rekayasa Industri (Rekind) is a national market leader in EPC with regional existence and global performance, with more than USD 2 billion worth of on-going contract and more challenging target in 2014, We would like to invite professionals from various disciplines to join us and become part of our nation’s better future.
Civil / Structural Engineer
Requirements
ADVERTISEMENT
Bachelor degree of Civil Engineering.
Min 10 years experience as a Civil / Structural Engineer in EPC Industries.
Preferable having experience combination type of work in site-construction or engineering.
Good communication in English
Teamwork & good communication skill
Piping Construction Engineer
Requirements
Bachelor degree of Mechanical / Material-Metalurgy Engineering.
Min 8 years experience as a Piping Construction Engineer in EPC Industries.
Preferable having experience combination type of work in site-construction or engineering.
Good communication in English.
Teamwork & good communication skill.
Cost Control / Estimate
Requirements
Bachelor degree of Engineering.
Min 7 years experience as a Cost Control / Estimate in EPC Industries.
Preferable having estimate experience in FEED projects.
Good communication in English.
Teamwork & good communication skill.
Project Risk Management Officer (Site)
Requirements
Bachelor degree of Engineering.
Min 5 years experience as a Project Risk Management / similiar type of jobs / duties in EPC Industries.
Having knowledge, experiece about HSE in EPC projects.
Able to stay in project site area.
Good communication in English.
Teamwork & good communication skill.
Project Risk Management Officer (HO)
Requirements
Bachelor degree of Industrial Engineering.
Min 5 years experience as a Project Risk Management / similiar type of jobs / duties in EPC Industries.
Having experience about managing risk management for projects and proposals.
Good communication in English.
Teamwork & good communication skill.
Tax Officer
Requirements
Bachelor degree of Economic, Tax, Accountancy, or relevan education background.
Min 5 years experience as a Tax Officer.
Preferable, having experience working in tax consulting.
Advance in computer operation for tax reporting.
Able to relocated to arround site.
Good communication in English
Teamwork & good communication skill
Purchaser-Expenditer
Requirements
ADVERTISEMENT
Bachelor degree of Instrument & Control (Physics) Engineering
Min 2 years experience as a Purchaser or Expenditer Staff
Advance in computer operation for reporting
Good communication in English
Teamwork & good communication skill
If you would like to take the challenge, please send your application, curriculum vitae and recent photograph to email below. Please write name, proposed position and Petromindo at the subject. for example: Wisnu Khoir_ Recruiter_Petromindo. Only short candidate and right email subject to be proceed.
